            Car Shopping Made Easy

            Welcome to Atlanta Toyota

            As a proud member of Penske Automotive Group, we are dedicated to serving all of your automotive needs. We aim to provide the best customer experience possible.

            Whether you're looking to experience the lasting reliability of the Toyota brand, turn to Atlanta Toyota.

            With a full selection of the latest new Toyota vehicles in stock, including the Corolla, Camry, RAV4, and many more. We're proud to be one of Duluth's premier Toyota dealerships. We serve customers throughout the Atlanta metro, from Duluth to Roswell and everywhere in between. Shop our selection online and get your purchasing process started. We also have a variety of Certified Pre-Owned Toyotas and used Toyotas. We also carry used cars from other automakers on our lot as well.

            Give us a call or stop by today to talk financing or to hear about our current specials. We can't wait to help drivers from Suwanee and surrounding regions find their new car, truck or SUV!

            Toyota Parts & Service

            We want to be there for you throughout the life of your vehicle. Atlanta Toyota is home to a state-of-the-art Parts & Service Department. Staffed with factory-trained and professional technicians, our Service Department will have your vehicle back on the road in no time. No matter what you're driving or where you bought it, we can help. For routine maintenance or more serious car repair, you can now schedule service appointments at Atlanta Toyota. You can also order genuine Toyota parts on our website.
